Dev --> UC14

' Pre-Tenant User
PreU --> UC01
PreU --> UC02

' ============================================
' USE CASE RELATIONSHIPS
' ============================================

' Include Relationships (dotted line with <<include>>)
UC01 ..> UC10 : <<include>>
UC02 ..> UC06 : <<include>>
UC04 ..> UC05 : <<include>>
UC14 ..> UC16 : <<include>>

' Extend Relationships (dotted line with <<extend>>)
